  "title": "Beautician cum Nail & Eyelash Technician #80831",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Beauty Salon</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Beautician cum Nail & Eyelash Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bukit Merah</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days/ 6 Days work week (10am – 10pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Commission + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide manicure and pedicure services.</li><li>Perform eyelash extension and eyelash lifting services according to client preferences.</li><li>Advise customers on suitable nail, lash and beauty services based on their needs and skin/condition.</li><li>Assist in providing facial treatments and body care / slimming / massage services under guidance and training.</li><li>Maintain high standards of hygiene and cleanliness for all tools, equipment and treatment rooms.</li><li>Build and maintain good relationships with customers to encourage repeat visits.</li><li>Assist with basic reception duties such as booking appointments, answering enquiries and handling payments when required.</li><li>Support day to day shop operations and any other ad hoc tasks assigned by the management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>With experience in nail art, eyelash extensions or beauty treatments is preferred.</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Responsible, hardworking and willing to learn new techniques</li><li>Able to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays.</li><li>Training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80831 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
